Class IloCplex.IntParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.Param
      • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.IntParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static class IloCplex.IntParam
extends IloCplex.Param
    Symbolic parameter names for integer-valued IloCplex parameters. For more detail about each parameter, see the CPLEX Parameters Reference Manual.

    Serialized Form
